{"id":158713,"type":1,"name":"番長連合","summary":"東照美、堂本勘二、横山修一らを中心とした大日本全学連合会（全学会、通称「番長連合」）が3年で全国制覇を成し遂げる過程を綴った物語。作品では、三中との抗争「橋船事件」、上総連合との抗争「千葉南北戦争」、池袋での神山との抗争「池袋戦争」が記録されている。全学会はそれらすべてに勝利を収め、後に全国制覇を成し遂げる。 　","info":"<li><span>册数: </span>16</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/12901\">阿部秀司</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span>秋田書店</li><li><span>连载杂志: </span>週刊少年チャンピオン</li><li><span>发售日: </span>2003-11-06</li><li><span>开始: </span>2003年</li><li><span>结束: </span>2006年</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"staff":[{"id":12901,"image":"","name":"阿部秀司","desc":"作者"}],"relations":[{"id":158719,"image":"","title":"堂本ルール","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/158719"}],"comic":[{"id":158703,"name":"番長連合 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/c7/9e/158703_jp.jpg"},{"id":158697,"name":"番長連合 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/58/41/158697_jp.jpg"},{"id":158698,"name":"番長連合 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/56/82/158698_jp.jpg"},{"id":158699,"name":"番長連合 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/08/dd/158699_jp.jpg"},{"id":158704,"name":"番長連合 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/43/cd/158704_jp.jpg"},{"id":158701,"name":"番長連合 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/60/50/158701_jp.jpg"},{"id":158700,"name":"番長連合 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":158702,"name":"番長連合 (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":158705,"name":"番長連合 (9)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/da/5a/158705_jp.jpg"},{"id":158706,"name":"番長連合 (10)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/7e/cd/158706_jp.jpg"},{"id":158707,"name":"番長連合 (11)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1c/b9/158707_jp.jpg"},{"id":158708,"name":"番長連合 (12)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f7/c4/158708_jp.jpg"},{"id":158709,"name":"番長連合 (13)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/93/2a/158709_jp.jpg"},{"id":158710,"name":"番長連合 (14)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/34/b4/158710_jp.jpg"},{"id":158711,"name":"番長連合 (15)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/57/f4/158711_jp.jpg"},{"id":158712,"name":"番長連合 (16)","image"